@sovereignty
title: Catalan Sovereignty
subtitle: No other institutional lever is as symbolic and powerful as pushing for further sovereignty than the Parlament
on-arrival: coming_from_parlament = true;

**On Catalan Sovereignty**

Despite the Parlament being legally limited in its powers, it is still symbolically the highest representative body of the Catalan people. Using that, we can still push for further action within its walls by passing laws allowing the Generalitat and other official bodies more options. It's no secret that, no matter how water-tight we make these, the Constitutional Court will most probably strike them down. 

- @parlament_sovereignty_declaration
- @parlament_international
- @parlament_local
- @parlament_non_binding_consultations
- @parlament_referendum
- @parlament_dui
- @parlament_options: Let us consider other options

